The '''AAP-II blaster box''' was a model of [[AAP blaster box]] manufactured by [[Briletto Company]] and utilized by [[BL-series Battle Legionnaire]]s. It was a rectangular weapon specifically created for use by droids, mounted on the Battle Legionnaire's chest or held in front of the body. It was a modestly powerful weapon much smaller than its successor, the [[AAP-IV blaster box]].

